  "html_size": 185956,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110156676246\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110156676246\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d9fbaf578a4557b1.png\" width=\"304\" height=\"202\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 304px; rheight: 202px\" id=\"20130114_239/isuhani_1358168058781abvPb_PNG/%C7%E3%B8%AE.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5D97C96')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d9fbaf578a4557b1.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&lt;이수한의원 추나교정치료&nbsp;치료사례&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">30대 초반 남자분이십니다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">치료전 증상은 허리통증 및&nbsp; 어깨결림이 6개월 전부터 있어서 고생했습니다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">물건을 들때 허리가 무너지는 느낌이들었고 엑스레이 결과 척추가 많이 서있다는 이야기를 들었습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">어깨는 자려고 누워 있음 쑤셔서 잠을 이루기 힘들었고 배개를 배면 목이 불편해서 항상 뒤척이곤 했습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/854a127a5f4787a8.png\" width=\"484\" height=\"322\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 484px; rheight: 322px\" id=\"20130114_162/isuhani_13581701253539Pj5c_PNG/%B8%F1.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5D97C96')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/854a127a5f4787a8.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000; COLOR: #ffffff; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">어깨높이가 달랐고 골반과 목뼈가&nbsp;많이 </span><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #777777; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000; COLOR: #ffffff; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">틀어져 있었는데 </span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #777777; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000; COLOR: #ffffff; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">추나요법으로 치료하면서&nbsp; 바로잡고&nbsp; 척추의 틀어짐도 바로잡았습니다</span><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000\">.</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #777777; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000\"></span></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #777777; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000\"></span></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #777777; FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ff0000\"></span></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\">항상 성심 성의껏 치료해주셔서 감사하게 생각하고 있습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\">치료뿐만아니라 삶의 조언까지 해주셔서 심리적 안정까지 주셔서 더욱효과가 좋은듯합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\">이수한의원 원장님께 진심으로 감사드립니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/659ec9603b2d3fd8.jpg\" width=\"366\" height=\"503\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 366px; rheight: 503px\" id=\"20130124_50/isuhani_1358991520047Y2sB4_JPEG/%C0%CC%C0%E7%B9%CE_blog%BF%EB_%C6%ED%C1%FD.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5D97C96')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/659ec9603b2d3fd8.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bfc0851c3924b8e7.png\" width=\"201\" height=\"176\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 201px; rheight: 176px\" id=\"20130114_42/isuhani_1358170280361HBocf_PNG/%BF%E4%C5%EB.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5D97C96')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bfc0851c3924b8e7.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체,gulimche\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120724_85/isuhani_1343092976528P84XU_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 193px; rheight: 48px\" id=\"20120724_85/isuhani_1343092976528P84XU_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5D97C96')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120724_85/isuhani_1343092976528P84XU_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: cente